{"tid":2131896,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"給你煮光州的泡菜湯 - 陳 也","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:45:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91a9e6c1274758c9842a536eaf9eaf10d8deed0e","tid":2131896,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200721/DQVZEG74H5ERNPQIY44XBCFW7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200721%2FDQVZEG74H5ERNPQIY44XBCFW7E%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhAgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=c2089029\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200721%2FDQVZEG74H5ERNPQIY44XBCFW7E%2F&h=46cd2ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200721/DQVZEG74H5ERNPQIY44XBCFW7E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n給你煮光州的泡菜湯 - 陳 也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jij5d0e25yqsHAJojDKEG4OdivQ=/638x284/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W5GMBQ3HXVG5PEV4WSADCG3CPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJij5d0e25yqsHAJojDKEG4OdivQ%3D%2F638x284%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW5GMBQ3HXVG5PEV4WSADCG3CPY.png&h=08262ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝黃之鋒面書Newsis新聞圖片<br />\n<br />\n光州518民主運動40周年，由韓國通鍾樂偉引線，立場新聞報道，黃之鋒與當年犧牲的16歲學生文載學母親金吉子視像通話。。。。。。。。。。。。但載學因為得知同學兼摯友楊昌根在示威中被軍方槍殺身亡，堅守不肯離開。最終，載學遭前來鎮壓清場的軍警以M-16步槍射殺。十天後屍首才被家人尋回。<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞訪問比文載學和黃之鋒更年輕的「黃姑娘」，才12歲，經歷抗爭-19，「出得去就預咗被人拉，預咗傷，預咗死」。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">記者問理想中的12歲是怎樣的，她答：「生活得在香港呢個地方，就冇可能過一個正常嘅童年。因為對我來講，一個正常嘅童年，已經變咗係抗爭。」黃母是網媒記者，指女兒過去大半年沒喊，疫下停課期間，谷盡後釋放，每天都哭。</span></span>這些年輕人是Bob Dylan歌詞中born on the wrong side of the railroad track嗎？禁唱榮光，來一首光州的「獻給你的進行曲」：直至新時代到來的那天前，絕勿動搖！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d89028f231c507aeaaf128d63c567d2719179bc","tid":2131896,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"記者問理想中的12歲是怎樣的，她答：「生活得在香港呢個地方，就冇可能過一個正常嘅童年。因為對我來講，一個正常嘅童年，已經變咗係抗爭。」黃母是網媒記者，指女兒過去大半年沒喊，疫下停課期間，谷盡後釋放，每天都哭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bc055f31dbb14d66a6403491825ebafbd2161a","tid":2131896,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:34:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a66c4b6b62cef90ec81360c0597a92b400039c0e","tid":2131896,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5d89028f231c507aeaaf128d63c567d2719179bc","tid":2131896,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"記者問理想中的12歲是怎樣的，她答：「生活得在香港呢個地方，就冇可能過一個正常嘅童年。因為對我來講，一個正常嘅童年，已經變咗係抗爭。」黃母是網媒記者，指女兒過去大半年沒喊，疫下停課期間，谷盡後釋放，每天都哭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}